Frequently Asked Questions

Everything you need to know about the product and billing.
What services does Spines offer for authors?

Spines offers a complete range of publishing services to help bring your book to life. Our offerings include book formatting, professional editing, custom cover design, digital ebook creation, audiobook production, ghostwriting, and print-on-demand (POD) publishing.

We also provide copyright certification, global book distribution, and built-in marketing tools to support your launch and ongoing promotion.

Every author gets access to a customizable landing page and an easy-to-use dashboard to manage their book and track progress. For special requests or guidance, our publishing consultants are ready to assist at any stage.

How does the self-publishing process work with Spines?

Publishing with Spines is a simple and straightforward way to self-publish your book. Just upload your manuscript, polish it using our AI-powered editing tools, and format it for professional print, ebook or audiobook distribution. You can also create marketing campaigns using our built-in tools to help promote your book.

Everything is managed through a single, intuitive dashboard, giving you full control over your publishing journey, while our team is always available if you need extra support.

Can I try Spines for free?

Yes! Anyone can sign up for a free account by clicking the Get Started button at the top of the page. Try out our platform tools and see how easy it is to proofread, design your cover, and publish your book with Spines.

Can I use only some services instead of a full package?

At Spines, we offer three publishing packages, each designed to meet different author needs and publishing goals. Individual services arent available separately, but each package includes a range of features, such as editing, formatting, audiobook creation, and marketing support, depending on the level you choose.

You can select the package that best fits your project, and you always have the option to upgrade if your needs grow over time.

How long will it take to publish my book with Spines?

With Spines, the entire publishing process typically takes around 30 days, from the moment you choose your plan until your book appears on Amazon.

Keep in mind, the timeline can vary depending on your needs. If you choose to work with our professional team for additional serviceslike translation, line editing, illustration, ghostwriting, and moreyour publishing journey may take a bit longer to ensure top-quality results.

How much does publishing with Spines cost?

Spines offers three standard publishing plans, plus two specialized plans for authors focused on childrens literature. Each plan is designed to fit different publishing goals, budgets, and book formats.

The cost depends on several factors, including the length of your manuscript, the formats you choose to publish (ebook, audiobook, softcover, or hardcover), the level of personal support you prefer, and any additional services you might need.

Wherever you are in your publishing journey, theres a plan built to meet your needs. To find the best fit for your project, explore our pricing page or connect with one of our publishing experts for personalized guidance.

Does Spines provide a copyright certificate for my book?

Yes. When you upload your manuscript to Spines, we automatically generate a digital copyright certificate, giving you official proof of ownership and protecting your rights from day one.

Can I create an audiobook with Spines?

Yes! Spines makes it easy to turn your book into a professionally produced audiobook. Our platform guides you step-by-step through the creation process, from narration to final production, ensuring high-quality results.

Once completed, we handle distribution across major listening platforms like Audible and Spotify, helping you expand your reach and connect with new audiences around the world.

Does Spines offer marketing services for books?

Yes. Spines provides built-in book marketing tools to help you promote your book across major platforms like Amazon, Facebook, and Instagram. You can easily create targeted ad campaigns, launch promotional strategies, and track their performance directly from your dashboard.

Our tools are designed to simplify book marketing, helping you reach the right readers, boost visibility, and grow your sales.

Does Spines distribute my book?

Yes. Spines handles distribution for your book in both print and eBook formats across major online retailers like Amazon, Apple Books, Barnes & Noble, Kobo, and more. We make it easy for your book to be available to readers worldwide, while you maintain full ownership and control over your work.

Does Spines offer eBook publishing services?

Yes. Spines provides professional eBook creation, formatting, and publishing services, making it easy to create a high-quality digital version of your book. Your eBook can be distributed across major platforms like Amazon Kindle, Apple Books, Kobo, and more, helping you reach readers worldwide.
